        "faq_i3m3aL": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "margin_top": 32,
            "margin_bottom": 32,
            "gap": 0,
            "faq_content": "<title>1. Is this shorts really quick-drying?</title>\n<p>Yes. The fabric is designed to efficiently absorb and release moisture, helping sweat dry quickly and keeping you comfortable longer.</p>\n<title>2. Will it feel hot or stuffy in summer?</title>\n<p>No. The micro-texture structure improves airflow and breathability, helping reduce heat buildup even in warm conditions.</p>\n<title>3. How does it feel after sweating?</title>\n<p>It stays lightweight and dry. Moisture doesn’t linger on the surface, so you avoid that sticky, heavy feeling.</p>\n<title>4. What activities is it suitable for?</title>\n<p>It’s built for everyday movement, including commuting, travel, hiking, training, and casual wear.</p>\n<title>5. Is there secure storage for essentials?</title>\n<p>Yes. It features multiple pockets including side pockets and a hidden rear zipper pocket, designed to keep your essentials secure on the move.</p>",
            "target_tab": "faq"
          }
        },
